comments[6]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-03T16:16:50.033Z",codex-agent,Created after de-dup scan for SDK and Pi wrapper lifecycle parity scope.
  "2026-04-03T17:09:38.168Z",codex-agent,Extended shared SDK command contracts and Pi wrapper action/argument mapping for extension lifecycle actions including scope/github/ref parity.
  "2026-04-04T16:38:30.829Z",codex-agent,"Duplicate-check evidence: ran pm context --limit 10, pm search \"beads todos sdk parity\" --limit 20, pm list-open --limit 20, pm list-in-progress --limit 20, and pm get pm-9ajy; reusing existing feature item with no duplicate create. Audit finding: beads/todos relocation parity is intact, but SDK/Pi action contract for beads-import still requires file and does not expose preserveSourceIds."
  "2026-04-04T16:42:27.872Z",codex-agent,"Implemented SDK and Pi wrapper parity for beads-import: file is optional and preserveSourceIds is now exposed in shared action schema and CLI arg mapping. Verification: pnpm build passed; targeted unit suite passed (5 files, 77 tests); integration CLI suite passed (1 file, 52 tests)."
  "2026-04-05T01:12:17.371Z",codex-agent,"Reopened for Issues 2+7 follow-up: extend contracts output with per-action runtime invocability metadata and runtime-only filtering so schema universe and active runtime surfaces are explicit."
  "2026-04-05T02:19:16.984Z",codex-agent,"Issues 2+7 follow-up completed: contracts now emits per-action runtime availability metadata and supports runtime action filtering (`--runtime-only`, alias `--active-only`) with CLI/completion/contracts/Pi parity. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/unit/pi-agent-extension.spec.ts passed; contracts repro probe with --no-extensions shows runtime_only=true, beads-import filtered from runtime actions, and full output action_availability marks beads-import as extension-disabled; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed (branch 91.01%); pnpm build passed."
